OL,3,CJury sworn in for trial of man accused
OL,4,Cof murdering his one-month-old son
OL,6,FA jury has been sworn in for the trial
OL,7,Fof a man accused of killing his one-
OL,8,Fmonth-old son.
OL,10,FTony Bartlett, 39, denies charges of
OL,11,Fmurder and manslaughter relating to
OL,12,Fthe death of Atticus Bartlett.
OL,14,FAtticus was four weeks old when he was
OL,15,Ftaken to hospital in a critical
OL,16,Fcondition. He died on 23 July 2022.
OL,18,FOn Thursday, a jury of six men and six
OL,19,Fwomen was sworn in to try the case at
OL,20,FBristol Crown Court.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
