OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781277116
OL,3,CJury sworn in for trial of man accused
OL,4,Cof murdering his one-month-old son
OL,6,FMr Justice Cavanagh told the jury that
OL,7,Fthe trial would be opened by the
OL,8,Fprosecution on Friday.
OL,10,FThe judge said: "The case involves the
OL,11,Fdeath of a four-week-old baby. The
OL,12,Fprosecution allege that the defendant
OL,13,Fwas involved in the murder of the baby.
OL,15,F"He denies that allegation. It is a
OL,16,Fsensitive case and some of the
OL,17,Fevidence may be distressing."
OL,26,@rD@QOUwD@AOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
