PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781277116
OL,3,CJury sworn in for trial of man accused
OL,4,Cof murdering his one-month-old son
OL,6,FThe judge told jurors that it was not
OL,7,Fpossible to give an exact time
OL,8,Festimate for the case but it is
OL,9,Fbelieved it will last for up to five
OL,10,Fweeks.
OL,12,FCharles Row KC and Sarah Jenkins are
OL,13,Fappearing for the prosecution.
OL,14,FBartlett is represented by Nigel Power
OL,15,FKC and Ian Morrell.
OL,17,FAvon and Somerset Police previously
OL,18,Fsaid officers were called by
OL,19,Fparamedics to an address in Chard,
OL,20,FSomerset, at about 11.30pm on 16 July
OL,21,F2022.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
