PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781277116
OL,3,CJury sworn in for trial of man accused
OL,4,Cof murdering his one-month-old son
OL,6,FThe baby was taken to hospital in a
OL,7,Fcritical condition and died on 23 July.
OL,9,FBartlett, of Axminster, Devon, denies
OL,10,Fthe two charges against him and the
OL,11,Ftrial continues.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
